text: Yeh Dil Chahe More is an Indian television series which aired on STAR One from 19 December 2005 to 26 October 2006. == Cast == * Chandana Sharma as Tara Arora * Amit Khanna as Veer Pratap Singh * Avtar Gill as Jagmohan Arora * Supriya Karnik as Shashi Arora * Baba Sehgal as Akshay Arora * Kushal Punjabi as Rahul Arora * Neelu Kohli as Billo * Aparna Tilak as Mitali * Abir Goswami as Paramjeet Singh * Nasirr Khan ==References== == External links == * Official Website Category:Indian television soap operas Category:Star One (Indian TV channel) original programming Category:2005 Indian television series debuts Category:2006 Indian television series endings Category:2000s Indian television series
